data.title: J.D. Hayworth
data.meta_description: J.D. Hayworth. Actor: Scout 10-5. J.D. Hayworth was born on 12 July 1958 in High Point, North Carolina, USA. He is an actor, known for Scout 10-5 (2021), The War Room with Michael Shure (2012) and Die Fernseh-Pressekonferenz (1947). He has been married to Mary Yancey since 1989. They have three children.
